{
  "texts": [
    "Further, the approximation of the geometry is rather poor compared to the previously shown test cases.",
    "No subsequent geometry refinement was employed to keep the number of cells to a minimum.",
    "Since the first modes typically capture large, dominant flow structures, refining the grid near the aircraft model has a minor impact on the SVD results and can therefore be omitted here.",
    "(11a) further shows cells located inside the geometry, which should have been marked as invalid and removed during the refinement process.",
    "A possible reason why these cells are not removed is a compression step of the STL file representing the aircraft half-model, carried out before starting the refinement process."
  ]
}